         <abstract id="aspace_3ad7538b7e3fe5f112637a2dc9c22024">The collection consists of manuscript and typescript material created by Frederick Stoever Dickson and others pertaining to Dickson's research on the life and work of William Makepeace Thackeray; included are letters to Dickson from authors, librarians, publishers, and other colleagues.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/nr90011160"
                      rules="aacr"
                      source="naf">
               <part>Dickson, Frederick Stoever, 1850-1925</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
